## 🩺 The Diagnosis System (The Magic Part)

This is what makes the system special. Instead of guessing when fences need staining, the computer calculates it based on science.

### What It Considers:
- **Wood Type:** Fences need staining more often than decks
- **Weather:** Sunny fences fade faster than shaded ones
- **Damage:** Cracks and mold mean more frequent service
- **Moisture:** Wet areas need more protection
- **Age:** How long since last staining

### The Result:
Instead of "come back next year," you get:
- "🟢 Excellent - due in 30 months"
- "🟡 Good - check in 12 months"
- "🟠 Needs attention - schedule in 3 months"
- "🔴 Urgent - needs service now!"

### Why This Matters:
- **You don't miss jobs** (customers forget to call)
- **You charge fair prices** (damaged fences cost more)
- **Customers are happy** (you prevent expensive repairs)
- **You make more money** (predictive service = repeat business)

