## 🚨 Common Problems & Solutions

### "Command not found"
- You need to install Node.js first
- Or add it to your computer's PATH

### "Database connection failed"
- Make sure PostgreSQL is running
- Check the database name and password in settings

### "Page won't load"
- Make sure the server is started (`pnpm run dev`)
- Check that port 5173 isn't blocked

### "I don't understand something"
- Look for help buttons in the app
- Check the documentation files in this folder
- Start with just adding one customer - learn gradually

